    <h1>Zo√©, will you be my Valentine? üíñ</h1>

    <div class="buttons">
      <button id="yes">Yes</button>
      <button id="no">No</button>
    </div>

    <div class="note">The ‚ÄúNo‚Äù button is not an option üòà</div>
